snippet.title: Project Cradle Beta Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
I'm excited to announce that a fancy new build for my game, Project Cradle, is now live!!
Project Cradle is a momentum platformer, inspired by games like Sonic 3, Donkey Kong Country and Portal! Please, like and wishlist it here:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2757950/Project_Cradle/
You can also play this demo in-browser and on android, at projectcradle.net
